official_title: A bill to amend the Public Health Service Act to revise the migratory health program under that act so that seasonal agricultural workers will be provided services on the same basis as migratory agricultural workers.

summary.text: Amends the Public Health Service Act to entitle seasonal agricultural workers to the same migratory health program services furnished to migratory agricultural workers.

titles.title: A bill to amend the Public Health Service Act to revise the migratory health program under that act so that seasonal agricultural workers will be provided services on the same basis as migratory agricultural workers.
